=== GLOWING_ARTIFACT ===
# id: 0
# title: The Glowing Artifact
# chinese_title: 光物
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

A faint luminescence draws your eye to a crevice in the station wall. Wedged between corroded panels, a crystalline object pulses with an inner light. The glow shifts between blue and gold, casting strange shadows across the corridor. Your scanner picks up unusual energy readings.

* [Carefully extract the artifact]
  ~ gain_radical("光")
  "光" (guāng) — light, brightness
* [Scan it with your equipment first]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "扫" (sǎo) — to scan, to sweep
* [Leave it undisturbed]
  ~ nothing
  "安" (ān) — peace, safety
